<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Account Activation</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div>
        <p>Hi,</p>
        <p>Thank you for registering with us. To activate your account, please use the following activation code:</p>
        <span class="activation-code"><%= activation_code %></span> <!-- Make sure this matches the key in your data object -->
        <p>If you did not request this email, please ignore it.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        <p>Thank you!</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
